name: Simple 1500 Jitsuyou Series Vol. 11: Katei de Dekiru Tsubo Shiatsu
overview: Simple 1500 Jitsuyou Series Vol.11 - Katei de Dekiru Tsubo Shiatsu is the eleventh game in the practical 1500 series released for the Playstation One console by D3 Publisher. This time the game let the user to check a complete shiatsu encyclopedia with big descriptions and also images.
